args: Ohmigosh, whaaaat? A castle in a forest?\nThat's so mystical, I can't EVEN!
*sigh* Well, that took a while,\nbut it's nice to finally be home.
That was a rather strong batch of\nopponents today; I'm finding myself\nmore worn out than normal.
Prithee, hold. A lone figure\nstands before the gate.
If I snap it at a dramatic low angle...\nOhmigosh, it looks SO good!\nI'm like my very own hype man!
Oh, heya! You must be the castle peeps,\nyeah? Hope you don't mind me snappin'\na few pics of your digs!

Oh, right! Lemme introduce everybody.
This magical device here is Clix—he's
from another world, and he has the
ability to take pictures, which are...
Y'know what? It's gonna be faster if I\njust show you. Group selfie!
I have zero idea what is\nhappening right now.
Look, don't worry about it, yeah?\nJust stand here next to me.
Squeeze in good and tight, guys!\nWe all gotta get in the frame!
And boom! We just snapped a pic.\nLooks pretty rad, huh?
That's amazing... Guys, look! LOOK!\nWe're all on that little slate!
The details in this painting\nare extraordinary...
How did you draw it so fast?
Yeah, I didn't really DRAW it so much\nas it sorta...um...transcribed it?

See, Clix here uses light mana to turn
whatever he's looking at during that
exact moment into a permanent image.
Isn't it freakin' AMAZEBALLS?!
Could the design of that device be...?
Oh, hey there! I'm Nadine. Who're you?
Zounds, but you approached quickly!\nYet as to your query, I am Nefaria,\na denizen of this estate.
Wait, you live HERE? That's amazing, 'Ria!\nYou must be a princess or whatever.

Leaving aside your form of address
for the nonce, I am no one of note.
That man there, however, is a prince
of the highest quality.
Wait, SERIOUSLY?! Holy wowsers, I've\nnever met anyone this crazy fancy before.\n...Hey, prince dude! Let's get another pic!

Guys, I can BARELY handle this castle.
I mean, I know it's my first time here
or whatever, but I still feel all totally
wistful and memory-y about it.

It's like I'm home, but not my actual
crappy home—it's more like the home
I always WANTED to be my home!
*sniff* Oh man, I'm totes gonna bawl.
Uh, it was Nadine, right?\nWhere are you from, exactly?
Oh, just a dry little desert\nwaaaay south of here.

But we moved around a lot, so I can't
really say, like, THIS specific place is
where my home is, but I guess— Whoa!
The sun's already setting!

Look, I totally wanna keep chatting you
guys up, but it's gonna be all dark soon.
You mind if I crash at your castle tonight?
Pleeeeeeease?
You can stay here as long as you like.
Aw, you're the BEST, prince dude!
Er, that's okay with everyone, right?
If such be your will, then we\nshall of course see it done.
In that case, welcome aboard, Nadine.
Guys. You are all. THE BEST!
